author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Bishop Briggs, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when she visited The Current studio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 The Way I Do
00:04:15 Wild Horses
00:07:38 River

Musicians
Bishop Briggs — vocals
Nicholas Hughes — drums
Mark Jackson — guitar 
Ian Brennan Scott — keyboard

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark, Jalen Russell
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
